        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What happens if a couple has different love languages?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Having different love languages is very common. The key to success is for each partner to learn to 'speak' the other's language, even if it feels unnatural at first."
